data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom ranch-style home, perfectly positioned on a generous corner lot in the heart of Hartsville. Located within walking distance to the local high school, this property offers the ideal blend of convenience and tranquility for your family.  Spread out over a single, expansive level, this home features a thoughtful layout that includes a formal living room, a formal dining area, and a large den, all designed for comfortable living and entertaining.  The backyard is a true highlight, featuring a pool and a basketball court, promising endless fun and relaxation for the whole family. Whether it's cooling off on hot summer days or enjoying a game of basketball, this backyard has something for everyone.  A two-car garage, a dedicated office and ample storage throughout the home ensure practicality matches the comfort and style of this stunning property.  This ranch-style home in Hartsville is more than just a house; it's a lifestyle. With its prime location, family-friendly layout, and exceptional outdoor amenities, it's ready to be the backdrop for your family's best memories. Don't miss the opportunity to own this slice of Hartsville heaven. Schedule your viewing today and step into your dream home tomorrow.  Contact your local agent and schedule a private showing!!
